1
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:05,000
Not hanging out with friends after school?

2
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:09,480
I feel like we haven't really had a proper talk yet.

3
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:11,160
Talk about what?

4
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,840
The past.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:15,160
Things were so chaotic when our parents remarried.

6
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:17,000
We don't really know each other that well, do we?

7
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,720
Actually, I do.

8
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:22,280
You weighed 3,560 grams when you were born.

9
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:23,800
And you took your first steps when...

10
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:24,800
Gross.

11
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,320
Seriously, that's creepy!

12
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,400
Your mom told me when she was drunk.

13
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:31,200
That old lady...

14
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:35,240
I lived alone with Dad for a while.

15
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:38,200
I was definitely shocked when I heard he was remarrying.

16
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:40,920
But I figured as long as he's happy, that's all that matters.

17
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,400
For real?

18
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:43,920
Watching my mom and stepfather all lovey-dovey...

19
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:46,840
It's a pretty complicated feeling.

20
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,680
Isn't it nice to have a great older brother?

21
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,920
I mean, sure...

22
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,880
But that's not how it is at all!

23
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:01,400
Anyway, we'll go our separate ways after graduation.

24
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:04,000
Until then, let's just try to get along as brothers.

25
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,000
Let's get along!

26
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:09,080
What are your plans after graduation?

27
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:11,840
Probably college, I guess?

28
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,800
Are your grades good enough?

29
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,600
I should be fine for my top choice.

30
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:17,840
Ugh, show-off.

31
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,160
What about you?

32
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:22,720
I was planning on a track scholarship.

33
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:25,760
But now I'm having second thoughts.

34
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:29,200
How about I tutor you?

35
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:32,240
Oh, right! Why didn't I think of that?

36
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,680
Mizuki and I went to the same middle school.

37
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,640
He was so outgoing back then.

38
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:40,520
But once he got to high school, he just stopped socializing...

39
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,440
Is there something you're hiding from me?

40
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,480
Huh?

41
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:52,840
Like something that's bothering you?
